{"tid":2402177,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"男子被控去年大埔阻街 今於粉嶺法院被裁定罪成 還押候判","createTime":"2021-02-10T09:20:00.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-10T13:04:48.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"cc28548faf8ac2fc08d4e5a0d7da0cbd599701bb","tid":2402177,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T09:20:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/13603\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F13603&d=9j7BdtwWq97OJFdF2FXGhW8HdWgMvHIPJs6XZvMXZMw%3D&h=72f8989e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/13603</a><br />\n<br />\n#粉嶺裁判法院第六庭 <br />\n#黃國輝裁判官<br />\n#20200308大埔 #裁決<br />\n#阻街<br />\n<br />\n陳(38)<br />\n<br />\n控罪：在公眾地方造成阻礙。<br />\n（香港法例第228章簡易程序治罪條例第4A條）<br />\n<br />\n案情：<br />\n於2020年3月8日在大埔安祥路大元街市外近燈柱EB370無合法權限或辯解留下一塊木卡板，兩個膠籃及雜物於路上，可能對上述地方或人造成阻礙。<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n速報：<br />\n法庭宣布罪成‼️索取背景報告，期間還押‼️<br />\n<br />\n押後至2月24日930 於粉嶺裁判法院1號庭判刑。"},{"pid":"2eee537a7480e9f6def710f3374c48ada0c043f2","tid":2402177,"uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T09:20:59.000Z","msg":"有市民為反對政府將大埔賽馬會普通科門診診所定為指定診所，於去年3月8日在大埔集結並堵路，一名男裝修工人指揮他人用木卡板和膠籃等雜物堵路被捕，經審訊後被裁定一項公眾地方造成阻礙罪成。黃國輝裁判官指，被告當日曾先後用手指向人和馬路，隨即便有人手持卡牌走到馬路，可見其有指揮他人的行為。黃官將案件押後至2月24日判刑，以索取背景報告，期間被告須還押。<br />\n<br />\n黃官裁決時指，被告在一開始過馬路時，有抬高左手，之後動作有改變。在行過一棵樹後，手便放下了。期間，雖然未能看清楚其動作，但明顯有動作，與控方第一證人的口供不衝突。另雖控方第2證人稱見不到被告左手有動作，惟黃官指被告動作改變的時間只有1至2秒，見不到也不足為奇，因而認為兩人證供清晰有條理，接納兩人證供。<br />\n<br />\n黃官續稱，當日被告站在行人路邊，先指向人，再指向馬路，然後就有人將卡板放在馬路中心。片段中亦清楚見到，被告曾與另一名將雜物擺放到馬路的男子，一起走到卡牌的位置，逐裁定其一項公眾地方造成阻礙罪成。<br />\n<br />\n辯方求情時指，被告現年38歲，為工程項目經理，持有浸大工商管理文憑。他的母親及弟弟分別患有抑鬱症及精神病，被告每個星期會去探望2人3次。被告與太太育有一個5歲的兒子，家人關係融洽，其上司亦指被告對工作充滿熱情，態度認真。"},{"pid":"1bcea92e888dfabe8ce29aea8623380769e82aa1","tid":2402177,"uid":1988,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T09:22:08.000Z","msg":"阻街要還押<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fab24e5edb43ce85e30f2bba2a43a7663158e1df","tid":2402177,"uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1bcea92e888dfabe8ce29aea8623380769e82aa1","tid":2402177,"uid":1988,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T09:22:08.000Z","msg":"阻街要還押<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T09:24:11.000Z","msg":"好快衝紅燈都冇得保釋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa58d01f9cf8abfbae2bc3d616c775e99457b93a","tid":2402177,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T09:25:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ac9e7eb36d0240abcfcd16db1357bc0f16f84d8","tid":2402177,"uid":57862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T09:26:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b72cfe69d7e07895021bfddd74f16a1c902a227","tid":2402177,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T09:31:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4755a475590efdab8fdb5a4709d605faa8489881","tid":2402177,"uid":8566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T09:38:29.000Z","msg":"屌你阻街都入冊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f3d059ca97fa367ce80d20e2a70d95656b60a33","tid":2402177,"uid":204231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score